title: Top Dogs: Battle of the Undefeated
description:
The crew looks into this weekend's upcoming matchups, headlined by an undefeated Tennessee against an undefeated Georgia. Additionally, Alabama and LSU face off in a Death Valley showdown. Next, Wendi takes a look at the Wendy's Weekend Wakeup, focusing on notable HBCU matchups, including Howard vs North Carolina Central, and Southern vs Florida A&M. Finally, Wendi, Sam and Steve give their predictions for week 10 on "What a Weekend It Would Be."

itunes:subtitle: Wendy Nix, Sam Acho, and Steve Coughlin discuss upcoming matchups going into week 10 with special guest Mark Schlabach joining the show.
